TEXT.S:
Haiduan Nsgan Haiduan o gaga Nsgan Taitung, kmpraan kana dxgal o 892.99 km², (dxgal dgiyaq o 817.5 km², dxgal pmblxan o 74.18 km²). kmhbragan hiyi o 4,278, sapah o 1,090, seejiq tnpusu 4,032 hiyi, knhbragan hiyi o 94%(Bunung). Bunung ka hbaraw balay alang hini.
nyusan qpahan Nsgan Haiduan o niqan 6 alang ni maxal 15. 15 o, Kanahcian, Kanaluk, Bacingul, Kamcing, Kusunuki, Haitutuan, Takinusta, Sulai-iaz, Samuluh, Tuapuu, Takimi, Likau-uan, Bulbul, Vahu, Litu.
